Ifill family
going back decades. And Yamiche
Alcindor of

28:40.319 --> 28:43.522 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The New York Times, Gwen was a
mentor to her.

28:43.555 --> 28:46.725 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Pastor Lamar, I want to start
with you. You
knew Gwen in a way that none of
us at the

28:46.758 --> 28:52.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
table did. Besides the church
every weekend,
coming up through the church,
the Ifill name

28:52.998 --> 28:54.766 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
meant something.

28:54.800 --> 28:56.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REV. WILLIAM LAMAR IV, Pastor,
Metropolitan
African Methodist Episcopal
Church: Indeed.

28:56.702 --> 29:00.238 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Gwen's father was the
secretary-general of
our denomination. So, all
official denominational

29:00.272 --> 29:03.976 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
literature and statistical
reports carried
his name.

29:04.009 --> 29:10.015 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I don't remember a time not
seeing or
knowing the Ifill name. And as I
came through

29:10.048 --> 29:14.987 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the ranks of ordained ministry,
her brother,
Presiding Elder Earle Ifill of
the Atlanta

29:15.020 --> 29:20.726 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
North-Georgia annual conference,
