voice and leader in our
denomination.

29:20.759 --> 29:26.131 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, when I had the privilege of
pastoring
her, I knew her pedigree and
knew her ancestry.

29:26.164 --> 29:27.966 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And she was a
woman of deep
faith.

29:28.000 --> 29:32.604 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REV. WILLIAM LAMAR IV: Oh, she
was there every
week. She was generous. She was
loving. She

29:32.638 --> 29:38.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
