mentor. And little
girls could come to her and hug
her, and she

29:38.510 --> 29:41.446 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
would share and she would
encourage. She was
a great gift to our community.

29:41.480 --> 29:46.485 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Rick Berke, you
were -- as
we just said, you knew Gwen
going back to

29:46.518 --> 29:51.223 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the 1980s as a young reporter.
Tell us a little
bit about that.

29:51.256 --> 29:54.359 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD BERKE, Executive Editor,
STAT: Gwen
and I covered City Hall together
35 years

29:54.393 --> 29:58.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ago at The Baltimore Evening
Sun. Then, years
later, we covered the White
House together

29:58.497 --> 30:00.365 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
at The New York Times.

30:00.399 --> 30:04.836 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, we have covered a lot of
politicians together.
And she had them quaking in
their boots.

30:04.870 --> 30:06.672 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

30:06.705 --> 30:10.308 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD BERKE: I mean, she would
look at them,
and they would be intimidated,
from mayors

30:10.342 --> 30:12.077 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to presidents.

30:12.110 --> 30:17.282 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But it was because she was
whip-smart, she
knew what to ask, and she was
relentless.

30:17.315 --> 30:23.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But she would always come back
with her big
smile that would just melt
everyone. So, she

30:23.088 --> 30:28.794 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
was tough, but she was
accessible. And she
always knew what she was talking
about. She

30:28.827 --> 30:33.799 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
would be able to synthesize the
news in a
way no one else I have ever seen
was able

30:33.832 --> 30:35.167 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
to.

