33:31.276 --> 33:32.244 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Yes.

33:32.277 --> 33:33.245 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
RICHARD BERKE: Right.

33:33.278 --> 33:34.913 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Yamiche -- go
