Niche? Like, what do you want to
be called?"

34:38.076 --> 34:39.277 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

34:39.311 --> 34:41.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
YAMICHE ALCINDOR: "Don't let
people give you
nicknames."

34:41.146 --> 34:43.682 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it really stuck with me,
