name. Know what
you want people to call you and
really believe

34:53.458 --> 34:55.226 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
in that.

34:55.260 --> 34:58.964 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And for my entire career, which
hasn't been
that long, she has really been
someone who

34:58.997 --> 35:03.501 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
