but someone who would watch my
"Meet the Press"

35:03.535 --> 35:05.337 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
interviews.

35:05.370 --> 35:07.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I remember the first time I was
