that are younger
than me up.

35:28.593 --> 35:32.197 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that is something that, even
in my busiest
days, I try to remember that she
took the

35:32.230 --> 35:35.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
time out to talk to me, so I
