someone who has really believed
in mentoring

35:43.575 --> 35:45.343 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
journalists coming behind her.

35:45.377 --> 35:51.416 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Pastor Lamar, you
