Gwen mentoring younger women at
the church.

35:51.449 --> 35:53.885 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What was it about her? How did
those connections
work?

35:53.918 --> 35:59.624 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REV. WILLIAM LAMAR IV: Well, I
think it's
important to say, Judy, that
Gwen comes from

35:59.657 --> 36:07.699 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
