shrink the
average human being.

36:11.469 --> 36:17.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, she comes from Barbados, the
West Indies,
and there's a great tradition of
excellence,

36:17.842 --> 36:23.381 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a great tradition of making sure
that you
make your presence known and
your gifts are

36:23.415 --> 36:25.150 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
used.

36:25.183 --> 36:28.386 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so, coming from Barbados,
being a part
of the African Methodist
Episcopal Church,

36:28.420 --> 36:33.058 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
