and created
her.

36:41.232 --> 36:47.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, she strengthened the church
by her presence
and by her participation, when
she was able,

36:47.705 --> 36:54.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
taking the battleground when
necessary, offering
financial gifts, offering
mentorship, always

36:54.079 --> 36:55.880 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
a smile.

36:55.914 --> 37:01.953 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And I just think she was
incredibly graceful,
incredibly stern, and just a joy
to be around.

37:01.986 --> 37:09.094 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We talked about books. We talked
