persons that
she knew in a way that wasn't
off-putting.

37:12.730 --> 37:14.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: She often talked
about being
a P.K., preacher's kid.

37:14.966 --> 37:16.768 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
REV. WILLIAM LAMAR IV: Oh, yes.

37:16.801 --> 37:21.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I was teasing that many
