37:21.339 --> 37:22.307 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

37:22.340 --> 37:24.142 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

37:24.175 --> 37:25.477 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REV. WILLIAM LAMAR IV: And many
