truthful place.

37:41.793 --> 37:47.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what I am amazed about is
the number of
deep personal relationships that
she was able

37:47.532 --> 37:55.473 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to maintain. The persons who
have been gathering
today as she was with us for her
last moments,

37:55.507 --> 37:59.244 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
she touched them in deep, deep
ways. And I
