comfortable

38:10.188 --> 38:11.956 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in these situations.

38:11.990 --> 38:15.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RICHARD BERKE: She knew how to
