for one second from doing the
debates and

38:35.847 --> 38:37.615 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the convention coverage.

38:37.649 --> 38:45.590 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the toughness and the drive
